# Code owners for global-qa-tools
#
# Listed owners are automatically requested for review on PRs that touch the
# matching paths. If "Require review from Code Owners" is enabled on the main
# branch ruleset, their approval is also required to merge.
#
# NOTE: the LAST matching pattern wins (rules are not cumulative). A more
# specific rule fully overrides "*", so any owner that should apply to a
# subfolder must be repeated on that subfolder's line.
#
# Owners must have write access to the repo for the request to take effect.

